    .row
      .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
        .row
          .col-xs-6
            h3 The ability to READ remains a uniquely human skill
          .col-xs-6
            p
              | Scientists need your help. You can make it
              | easier for scientists to find the information
              | they need to discover cures faster.

        .row
          .col-xs-6
            p
              | You can fix it. The ability to READ remains
              | a uniquely human skill. You can help biomedical
              | researchers can find the information they need
              | to discover cures faster.

          .col-xs-6
            h3 Scientific Communication is Broken

        .row
          .col-xs-6
            h3 If you can READ, you can HELP.
          .col-xs-6
            p
              | The search for cures for all diseases is
              | limited by the ability of scientists to
              | consume and understand the rapidly expanding
              | ocean of biomedical literature.

